title: Love The Test Days, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO48
description: The days that you face a do-or-die, put-up-or-shut-up situation are the days that define us. Andy Frisella calls those "Test Days."  Successful people don't just learn to face those days with determination.  They learn to love them.
